{"word":"κάπετος","slug":"κάπετος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κάπετος</b></el> <el>(κάπετος, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>for <el>σκάπετος</el>, from <a href='S:σκάπτω'><el>σκάπτω</el></a>\n<p/><i>a ditch, trench</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>:— <i>a hole, grave</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}